==========================================
IF RAW SOURCE:

  autoreconf --install
  ./configure
  make

===========================================
IF PACKAGE:

To build and install:

  ./configure
  make
  make install

To find out more on how to use the SPHERLS packages see user manuals in
./docs/manuals

============================================
COMMON OPTIONS

useful options for debugging add 'CXXFLAGS="-g -O0"' to ./configure to
compile unoptimized version for debugging.

